H0.text: In Greek mythology who was the Queen of the Gods, also the wife and sister of Zeus. Demeter

H1.text: In Greek mythology who was the Queen of the Gods, also the wife and sister of Zeus. Rhea

H2.text: In Greek mythology who was the Queen of the Gods, also the wife and sister of Zeus. Gaia

H3.text: In Greek mythology who was the Queen of the Gods, also the wife and sister of Zeus. HERA

A4.text: In Greek mythology, she is queen of the twelve Olympians and Mount Olympus, sister and wife of Zeus

A5.text: In historical times, the majority of the Greeks recognized Hera as the consort of Zeus
